slower or faster or whatever.

25
00:01:14.180 --> 00:01:18.280
You get these very unpredictable
looking wave like patterns

26
00:01:18.280 --> 00:01:21.730
and you're like, why is my
GPU fast at certain multiples

27
00:01:21.730 --> 00:01:23.600
