1311
00:56:09.580 --> 00:56:11.800
And I've gotten
this entire tile.

1312
00:56:11.800 --> 00:56:16.860
Now imagine what happens
if I add one element extra

1313
00:56:16.860 --> 00:56:19.480
and the way the
matrix is laid out,

1314
00:56:19.480 --> 00:56:23.680
my tile start-- my burst
sections flow over.

1315
00:56:23.680 --> 00:56:26.800
So now what's happening
is when I load my tile,

1316
00:56:26.800 --> 00:56:28.270
I'm going to load
this first part.

1317
00:56:28.270 --> 00:56:29.270
And that's really great.

1318
00:56:29.270 --> 00:56:31.720
I get the entire first
